      "rationale": "All model inputs are traceable to primary measurements: elastic modulus and yield strength from uniaxial coupon testing (N=6, ASTM E8); screw geometry from CMM measurements of production screws (N=5); UHMWPE block modulus from compression testing per ASTM D695 (N=4). Input uncertainty distributions (normal for modulus, lognormal for yield strength, uniform for geometry tolerances) were propagated via the Sobol analysis. A complete input uncertainty budget is documented in the simulation plan appendix. Gradation 5: all inputs traceable to primary measurements, full uncertainty distributions assigned and propagated, budget documented.",
