      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 4,
      "rationale": "Eleven non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs were tested across two independent laboratories (Lab A: N=6, Lab B: N=5). All screws were drawn from a single production lot (Lot 2023-07-A) with CMM-verified dimensional conformance. UHMWPE test blocks were from a single material batch, compression-tested for modulus prior to assembly. Inter-laboratory variability was characterized by two-way ANOVA; no significant lab effect was found (p=0.31). Sample traceability chain is complete. Gradation 4: multi-lab testing, production-representative samples, dimensional verification, inter-lab statistical analysis.",
